### AI Task Orchestrator — Qdrant 手工验证 HTTP 流程
### 前置：
### 1. docker compose up -d（MySQL + RabbitMQ）
### 2. docker compose -f docker-compose.qdrant.yml up -d（Qdrant）
### 3. Spring Boot 使用 docker,qdrant profile 启动
### 默认仍使用 mock embedding（dimension=128），仅 VectorStore 切换为 Qdrant

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@documentId = 1

### 上传文档（multipart；参数名 file；仅 .txt / .md）
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----QdrantDemoBoundary

------QdrantDemoBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="qdrant-verification.md"
Content-Type: text/markdown

# Qdrant Manual Verification

[EVIDENCE:qdrant-verification]
This chunk is used to verify that document upload, mock embedding, Qdrant upsert and vector search work together.
------QdrantDemoBoundary--

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        client.global.set("documentId", response.body.documentId);
    }
%}

###

### 查询文档 chunks
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/{{documentId}}/chunks

###

### 生成 embedding 并 upsert 到 Qdrant（mock provider）
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/{{documentId}}/embeddings

###

### 语义检索 TopK（经 QdrantVectorStore）
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "verify Qdrant upsert and vector search",
  "topK": 5,
  "documentId": {{documentId}}
}

###

### 可选：Retrieval Evaluation（需将 expectedChunkIds 替换为真实 chunkId）
# POST {{baseUrl}}/evaluations/retrieval
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "documentId": {{documentId}},
#   "topKValues": [1, 3, 5],
#   "cases": [
#     {
#       "caseId": "qdrant-verify-001",
#       "query": "verify Qdrant upsert",
#       "expectedChunkIds": [1]
#     }
#   ]
# }
